cgames
======

My collection of games written on C

Install
```
git clone https://github.com/17seannnn/cgames.git
cd cgames
./build.sh
cgames
```

Information about games

Car Reaction
------------
Arcade game to train your reaction

Movement

Arrows
AD

csnake
------
Snake game on C language

Movement

Arrows
WASD
HJKL

Esc - leave the game
